{"tid":2346906,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Elkie退CLC手寫信「用簡體字」！　香港網友湧入狠酸：人民幣真香","createTime":"2020-12-30T15:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T01:55:17.000Z","uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"65da226ee4e8a3682d11162d5dabd14ff67fbb87","tid":2346906,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"南韓女團CLC香港成員Elkie（莊錠欣）向經紀公司CUBE娛樂提出解約，更透過律師函控訴公司因為管理人員發生異動，已經明確表明「不再支持CLC發展」，30日正式以中、韓、英三種語言上傳手寫信感謝粉絲，其中中文版本的信是以簡體字撰寫，然而此舉卻引來不少香港網友諷刺她已經做好去大陸發展的準備，狠酸「人民幣真香」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5367/d5367972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5367%2Fd5367972.jpg&h=db4cefd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Elkie宣布向公司提出解約，退出CLC。（圖／翻攝Elkie IG）<br />\n<br />\nElkie在30日以中韓英三國語言寫下長篇手寫信，透露出道以來靠著粉絲的支持獲得很多力量，可惜很多時候「不是想做什麼就能做什麼」，常常感到力不從心，直言「我想為大家付出都做不到，真的讓我很傷心」，字字句句透露出無奈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5367/d5367970.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5367%2Fd5367970.jpg&h=9969e8af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5367/d5367969.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5367%2Fd5367969.jpg&h=915de7c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Elkie中文信。（圖／翻攝Elkie IG）<br />\n<br />\n其中，由於香港使用的是繁體字，但從小在當地受教育的Elkie中文信卻是以簡體字撰寫，讓許多香港網友感到失望，狂酸「人民幣真香」、「變愛國的Elkie了」、「香港讀書用的是繁體字，幹嘛用殘體字？」、「殘體字，要去奶共了...」、「連寫自己名字都用簡體字，北上的話就不（支持）了」等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5367/d5367971.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5367%2Fd5367971.jpg&h=55c3e831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Elkie貼文底下香港網友留言。（圖／翻攝Elkie IG）<br />\n<br />\n據悉，Elkie向CUBE娛樂提出解約，從她委託北京律師發出的律師函可看到，她在出道4年間發現公司多次違反合約內容，也未曾公開所有收入明細，且演唱會、商演等都沒有收到任何演藝收入的分成，僅拿到版權稅收入，此外，還透露CUBE由於管理人員發生異動，已經明確表明「不再支持CLC發展」。"},{"pid":"f65862f29802068437457aaea501c9ec35c9f2fe","tid":2346906,"uid":201604,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"支那種扮香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200553acef864ed5fada8d5765abb46da8b2a296","tid":2346906,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95732f44360282d3cdb1f90cda2ffea9a104a385","tid":2346906,"uid":215249,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:15:20.000Z","msg":"咁D通識老師夠用簡體啦又係支那人?"},{"pid":"3216b7614855b23cc17e08a643f8edb7bd6d0469","tid":2346906,"uid":140924,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:16:54.000Z","msg":"成件事同佢手字都幾肉酸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算啦，你估個個都做到的士陳咁成功咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5871e9645c3d4478e67d5c23b40bb273a1d09f5","tid":2346906,"uid":54608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:17:07.000Z","msg":"明顯唔係寫畀香港人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有乜好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ed6830c7a74db2b6060e33fea2a4ea0eddb383","tid":2346906,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"有啲字明明有簡體又寫返繁體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵人對一次先出街都唔識"},{"pid":"f4b07a0491d74